{"tid":499030,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我個fd算唔算係比人𡁻完鬆？應該分手？","createTime":"2017-12-14T11:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T14:03:14.000Z","uid":160050,"like":653,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"33869978cf5166d19e5e69265799b34886ab06a9","tid":499030,"uid":160050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"話說我個fd同我講佢同佢條仔拍拖就黎一個月<br />\n但係未扑野之前佢地都會成日一齊出街<br />\n直到扑完第一次之後 過幾日都無事<br />\n慢慢就開始無搵到我個fd 又成日失左蹤<br />\n個fd就話 佢條仔唔會同佢wts 又唔會傾電話<br />\nfd同我講 扑過唔止一次 仲要係無帶套<br />\n(女仔fd黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評：叫佢即刻分手 唔好再做免費雞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評：睇定啲先 話唔定遲啲會對佢好啲"},{"pid":"42932ef12a6309855ae29dc7c3eb385b65c9032f","tid":499030,"uid":51701,"like":248,"dislike":2,"score":246,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:04:16.000Z","msg":"1. 你朋友就是你<br />\n<br />\n2. 返5P 香討傾"},{"pid":"83a5d960f3337c334aff8cfa4e0e9cc62657b18f","tid":499030,"uid":38668,"like":105,"dislike":1,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:06:01.000Z","msg":"第一次就無套 個朕公廁味 格住個moon都feel到"},{"pid":"d5e0b5a56175a88ec88819b6e6dfcff50d659c0c","tid":499030,"uid":160050,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 你朋友就是你<br />\n<br />\n2. 返5P 香討傾</blockquote><br />\n認真唔是我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c8baca651efb5b376d65b8309303d1e3a34369","tid":499030,"uid":160050,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次就無套 個朕公廁味 格住個moon都feel到</blockquote><br />\n佢同我講係處 仲話咩一時情到濃時 <br />\n連套呢啲野都唔諗就扑左"},{"pid":"d9718a68d2beae9be19dd229ab7c5f7f29e9f433","tid":499030,"uid":74262,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fdeb66c6a01a24f4ab1a57321e38